	(13,1,'2014-04-01 15:21:01','2014-04-01 19:21:01','At The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology, we are thrilled to see our students graduate and move on to terrific new jobs in the cosmetology industry.\r\n\r\nBut that doesn’t mean we’re saying goodbye.\r\n\r\nOur alumni are active members of our cosmetology school\'s community – helping current students find new jobs, visiting as special guest lecturers, even coming back to work as instructors.\r\n\r\nWe want our alumni to <a title=\"Involvement\" href=\"http://www.theorloschool.com//alumni/involvement/\" target=\"_blank\">stay involved</a>, reach out for career assistance, and update us on current events and successes!','Alumni','','publish','closed','open','','alumni','','','2014-06-27 12:32:32','2014-06-27 16:32:32','',0,'http://www.theorloschool.com//?page_id=13',0,'page','',0),
