	(221,2,'2014-04-14 17:22:37','2014-04-14 21:22:37','The Orlo School of Hair Design and Cosmetology is an independent, privately-owned cosmetology school devoted to educating new cosmetology industry professionals. Our students move on to a variety of careers, from working as hairdressers, makeup artists and estheticians to owning independent beauty salons and representing major industry product companies.\r\n\r\nAt our cosmetology school, we’re interested not only in the creative aspects of cosmetology but the business of our industry, as well. Our students are prepared to start their own careers, and if they choose, to start their own businesses. While they learn how to style the looks of the individuals in front of them, they also learn how to attract new clients and how to retain them.\r\n\r\n<h3>There are a lot of beauty schools - why Orlo?</h3>\r\n\r\nWe know the decision about which beauty school to attend can be difficult, but we promise you this -\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<blockquote>We’re passionate about what we teach, and you can tell that as soon as you walk in our doors.\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n\r\nEvery day, we get to see new students pair their passion for beauty and design with skills that will help them succeed. Throughout our history, we’ve educated thousands of students who have received their cosmetology licenses from the New York State Board of Cosmetology and gone on to bright futures, and we look forward to many more years of education as a top beauty school ahead of us.','About','','inherit','open','open','','4-revision-v1','','','2014-04-14 17:22:37','2014-04-14 21:22:37','',4,'http://www.theorloschool.com//2014/04/4-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
